z^4=e^{i\left(4\theta+8k\pi\right)}=\cos(4\theta+8k\pi)+i\sin(4\theta+8k\pi)
Re(z^4)=-Im(z^4) \Rightarrow \cos(4\theta+8k\pi)= -\sin(4\theta+8k\pi)
\cos(\theta)=-\sin(\theta)
\theta=\frac{3\pi}{4}+\pi
